<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.3.6">
<l>antakaṉ ciṟuva ṉaracarta maracaṟ kiḷaiyava ṉaṇiyiḻai yaicceṉ</l>
<l>ṟentamak kurimai ceyeṉat tariyā temperu māṉaru ḷeṉṉa</l>
<l>cantamal kuḻalā ḷalakkaṇūṟ ṟuvarttam peṇṭiru meytinū liḻappa</l>
<l>vintiraṉ ciṟuvaṉ tērmuṉiṉ ṟāṉait tiruvallik kēṇi<supplied>k</supplied>kaṇ ṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When the younger brother of the king of kings, the son of the blind man,</l>
<l>Approaching the bejeweled one, said, “Do slave labor for us,”</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] when [she], being unable to bear [it],</l>
<l>Said, “Be gracious, our great lord,” as the wives of the one-hundred,</l>
<l rend="indent">feeling the distress of that dark-haired lady, lost their wedding threads,</l>
<l>The one who [then] stood at the front of the chariot of Indra’s son</l>
<l rend="indent">I saw at Tiruvallikkēṇi.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
